Name: Average resolution time for 'Completed + Cancelled'
Metric: The average of the duration between the start of the case and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Average time difference between 'Completed + Cancelled' and 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Total duration of 'Completed + Cancelled' activities in the event log
Metric: The sum of the duration between the start of the case and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Minimum time to reach 'Completed + Cancelled' from 'Accepted + In Progress'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Average time from 'Completed + Cancelled' to the next activity in a process variant
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Completed + Cancelled and the end of the case

Name: Total time spent in 'Completed + Cancelled' across all variants
Metric: The sum of the duration between the start of the case and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Average duration of 'Completed + Cancelled' in cases involving 'Accepted + Wait - User'
Metric: The average of the duration between the start of the case and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Average time from 'Accepted + In Progress' to 'Completed + Cancelled' across all variants
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Duration of 'Completed + Cancelled' in the context of the VINST system's incident and problem management process
Metric: The sum of the duration between the start of the case and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Longest time from 'Completed + Cancelled' to any subsequent activity
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Completed + Cancelled' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x000001E27CECF0A0> - AppliesTo.PROCESS

Name: Shortest time from any activity to 'Completed + Cancelled'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between the start of the case and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Average duration between 'Completed + Cancelled' and 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Completed + Cancelled' and activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'

Name: Total time from 'Completed + Cancelled' to 'Completed + In Call' across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Completed + Cancelled' and activity 'Completed + In Call'
